com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures

Class PhotoColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures.PhotoColor

  • public class PhotoColor
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represent the dominates colors in the photos. We use it to provide searching photos with colors. so we also hold the dominates colors in the photo.
